c: 20
v: 71
t: "(Firauni) Naboola mbu: “Ehh; mumusuubile neshili okhubafuchilila. Toto ye niye Omukhongo wenyu owabechesia obulosi. Kholano nditsa okhubateta emikhono chienyu nende amakulu kenyu buchikha ne nditsa okhubabaamba khumisala chietsitende, ne mulamanyakhwo mbu niwina mwifwe omululu weshinyasio shiokhutsililila"